# Calculate Performance Metrics
# Logistic Regression
logistic_regression_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, logistic_regression_predictions)
logistic_regression_precision = precision_score(y_test, logistic_regression_predictions, average='macro')
logistic_regression_recall = recall_score(y_test, logistic_regression_predictions, average='macro')
logistic_regression_f1 = f1_score(y_test, logistic_regression_predictions, average='macro')

# Decision Tree
decision_tree_accuracy = accuracy_score(y_test, decision_tree_predictions)
decision_tree_precision = precision_score(y_test, decision_tree_predictions, average='macro')
decision_tree_recall = recall_score(y_test, decision_tree_predictions, average='macro')
decision_tree_f1 = f1_score(y_test, decision_tree_predictions, average='macro')

# Random Forest

random_forest_precision = precision_score(y_test, random_forest_predictions, average='macro')

random_forest_f1 = f1_score(y_test, random_forest_predictions, average='macro')
